<title>USA: Schlumberger approves 2 for 1 stock split.</title>
<headline>Schlumberger approves 2 for 1 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Schlumberger Ltd said on Thursday that it approved a two-for-one stock split, which is reflected in the financial results it reported.</p>
<p>After the split, the company's first-quarter net income per share was $0.53, compared to $0.35 for the same period a year ago.</p>
<p>The split applies to shareholders of record as of June 2. Certificates will be mailed on or about July 11, the company said.</p>
